    <body>
        <p class="TableText">Opens a submenu, which lets you select a toolbar to open or close:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel"><MadCap:keyword term="Toolbars:Standard" />Standard </span>Opens or closes the Standard toolbar. <MadCap:snippetText src="../UIElements/StandardToolbarSummary.flsnp" /></li>
            <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Format </span>Opens or closes the Format toolbar.The Format toolbar lets you quickly apply formatting to images and objects in the Capture Editor. To see this toolbar, select <span class="Emphasis">View&gt;Toolbars&gt;Format</span>.</li>
            <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Layout </span>Opens or closes the Layout toolbar. The Layout toolbar lets you quickly sink, float, position, and align images and objects in the Capture Editor. To see this toolbar, select <span class="Emphasis">View&gt;Toolbars&gt;Layout</span></li>
        </ul>
    </body>
</html>